===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[point]] on the [[Earth]]'s [[surface]] directly above the [[focus]] of an [[earthquake]].
# (''figurative'') The [[focal point]] of any [[activity]], especially if [[dangerous]] or [[destructive]] .

